{"lemma":"حِصَّةٍ","slug":"حِصَّةٍ","root":"ح.ص.ص","root_slug":"ح-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8162","n8169"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"share, quota, ration, contingent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lesson, class"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stake, equity"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew חצי (khétsi, “half”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8162","headword_ar":"حَصَّهُ","root":"HS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~N","text_ar":"حَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, shaved it off;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, hair. (A, K, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~ati Alb~yoDapu raA^osahu","text_ar":"حَصَّتِ البّيْضَةُ رَاْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The helmet rubbed off his hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered his hair scanty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut off from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aArap","text_ar":"مَشَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", [a word for which I do not find any apposite meaning, and which is perhaps a mistranscription,] or with the shears: (Er-Rághib, as quoted in the TA:) whence, accord. to some, the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiS~apN","text_ar":"حِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~uwA bayonahumo raHimFA","text_ar":"حَصُّوا بَيْنَهُمْ رَحِمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severed, a tie of relationship between them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='ato sanapN faHaS~ato kul~a $aYo'K","text_ar":"جَا=ءَتْ سَنَةٌ فَحَصَّتْ كُلَّ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There came a dearth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a year of drought, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it did away with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consumed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destroyed, everything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~a Aljaliydu Aln~abota","text_ar":"حَصَّ الجَلِيدُ النَّبْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hoar-frost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rime, nipped, shrunk, shrivelled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blasted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burned,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoraqa","text_ar":"اَحْرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn:) a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Has~a","text_ar":"حَسَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~a","text_ar":"حَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", quasi-pass. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~ahu","text_ar":"حَصَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the first of the senses"},{"kind":"page_break","n":580},{"kind":"text","text":"explained above: see 7, in two places.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~aniY","text_ar":"حَصَّنِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlmaAli ka*aA","text_ar":"مِنَ المَالِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, * Msb, K, *) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a thing became my portion of the property:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came to me, and became my portion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came to me as my portion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~a","text_ar":"حَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [contr. to rule, by which it should be"},{"kind":"text","text":", the verb being intrans., unless the sec. pers. pret. be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSuSota","text_ar":"حَصُصْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~N","text_ar":"حَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) with which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuSaASN","text_ar":"حُصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., is syn., (S, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ran vehemently and quickly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSoHaSa","text_ar":"حَصْحَصَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSoHaSapN","text_ar":"حَصْحَصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was quick"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in going,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in journeying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pace."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~a","text_ar":"حَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSoHaSa","text_ar":"حَصْحَصَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in all its meanings; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kab~a","text_ar":"كَبَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kabokaba","text_ar":"كَبْكَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~a","text_ar":"كَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kafokafa","text_ar":"كَفْكَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Er-Rághib.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","A","K","S","AHn","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n8169","headword_ar":"حِصَّةٌ","root":"HS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of a sum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib:) and used to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion, lot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, Er-Rághib, K,) of food, and of beverage, and of land, &c.: (TA:) accord. to some, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~ahu","text_ar":"حَصَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ he cut off from it: ” (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiSaSN","text_ar":"حِصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}